Class EffUtilities

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container

              • gammaBetaMc.EffUtilities
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants

    public class EffUtilities
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    Utility class. Based on pre-computed efficiency (by Monte Carlo method) the sample activity is calculated. Also, one can perform crude estimation of experimental efficiency based on known source activity and compare this efficiency with the theoretical one (based on Monte Carlo simulation).
    Author:
    Dan Fulea, 11 Jul. 2005
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
